{"tid":2056319,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"路透社：港人向多間銀行查詢設離岸戶口　查詢增約三成","createTime":"2020-06-08T14:55:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-08T15:09:07.000Z","uid":39464,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"cd70694b49014d7cba4744f0a16e0308b2bfd13f","tid":2056319,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T14:55:43.000Z","msg":"路透社今日（8日）引述多位消息人士指，港人向多間銀行查詢開設離岸戶口的數量大幅上升，包括滙豐銀行，渣打銀行和花旗銀行，其中滙豐、渣打關於離岸戶口詢問量增加 25 至 35%。消息人士認為，這是由於港人對港區國安法的擔憂。<br />\n<br />\n消息人士指出，現時港人對離岸戶口的查詢增加，已拖慢了本地銀行的工作進度，並補充說新加坡、英國、悉尼和台灣等地區是受港人歡迎的地區。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95%E5%A3%93%E6%B8%AF-%E8%B7%AF%E9%80%8F%E7%A4%BE-%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E5%90%91%E5%A4%9A%E9%96%93%E9%8A%80%E8%A1%8C%E6%9F%A5%E8%A9%A2%E8%A8%AD%E9%9B%A2%E5%B2%B8%E6%88%B6%E5%8F%A3-%E6%9F%A5%E8%A9%A2%E5%A2%9E%E7%B4%84%E4%B8%89%E6%88%90/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%2589%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25A3%2593%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E9%2580%258F%25E7%25A4%25BE-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2590%2591%25E5%25A4%259A%25E9%2596%2593%25E9%258A%2580%25E8%25A1%258C%25E6%259F%25A5%25E8%25A9%25A2%25E8%25A8%25AD%25E9%259B%25A2%25E5%25B2%25B8%25E6%2588%25B6%25E5%258F%25A3-%25E6%259F%25A5%25E8%25A9%25A2%25E5%25A2%259E%25E7%25B4%2584%25E4%25B8%2589%25E6%2588%2590%2F&d=N73AYdKZ8ITSJgwUZ5%2B19q0J0iXDlbDdnmyxhWT3nOs%3D&h=1955d69f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%2589%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25A3%2593%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E9%2580%258F%25E7%25A4%25BE-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2590%2591%25E5%25A4%259A%25E9%2596%2593%25E9%258A%2580%25E8%25A1%258C%25E6%259F%25A5%25E8%25A9%25A2%25E8%25A8%25AD%25E9%259B%25A2%25E5%25B2%25B8%25E6%2588%25B6%25E5%258F%25A3-%25E6%259F%25A5%25E8%25A9%25A2%25E5%25A2%259E%25E7%25B4%2584%25E4%25B8%2589%25E6%2588%2590%2F&h=6db3f1bd